These are Puzzles for 6x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, mirinda
There are 2 different favourite colors: chestnut, turquise
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: thriller, zombie
There 2 different types of food: pear, spinach
City: nizza, hamburg
The people have 2 different hobbies: skydiving, video-games
1. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left##1
2. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
4. the person eating pear is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Beverage      | milk       | mirinda    |
| Color           | turquise | chestnut |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie     | thriller   |
| Food   | spinach  | pear     |
| City           | hamburg       | nizza     |
| Hobby     | skydiving     | video-games        |

