.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-2::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, pall-mall
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, march
2 different games are played: whist, monopoly
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, pop
2 different pets are kept: bird, rat
There are 2 different favourite colors: fuchsia, apricot
1. the fan of pop is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
2. the pall-mall-smoker is the fan of pop##1
3. the person playing whist is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
4. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |
| Cigar      | oliveros        | pall-mall   |
| Birthday         | march | may |
| Game   | whist     | monopoly   |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | pop     |
| Pet           | rat        | bird    |
| Color     | fuchsia  | apricot    |

