.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-3::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: april, september
There are 2 different favourite beverages: water, cola
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: martial-arts, superhero
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: salsa, hip-hop
2 different pets are kept: cat, guinea-pig
House: gothic-revival, townhouse
1. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person drinking water##1
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |
| Birthday          | september    | april      |
| Beverage         | cola   | water       |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | martial-arts |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | salsa    |
| Pet           | cat       | guinea-pig   |
| House         | townhouse   | gothic-revival     |

