.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-20::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: reading, dancing
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, swimming
City: london, liverpool
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, gospel
2 different pets are kept: ferret, snake
House: tower, colonial
1. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the fan of disco##1
2. the tower house is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
4. the person traveling to london is the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |
| Hobby      | reading    | dancing      |
| Sport          | badminton | swimming |
| City           | liverpool     | london      |
| Music-Genre   | gospel    | disco       |
| Pet           | snake     | ferret      |
| House     | colonial   | tower         |

 